parameters:
"Oh, my apologies, we're fully booked with reservations
recently. Please come again another day."
...Is that so? Understood. I'll come again next time.

"It will be 500 mon for one night. Will you be staying with
us?"
Yes. Then I'll be in your care tonight at this inn.
"Thank you very much. Please use the room in the middle."

--Karin was guided to a single room, where she relaxed
leisurely inside.
Hehehe...\I[15] She's really cute, isn't she.

--It's no wonder Karin looks terrified. Surprisingly, an
unknown man quietly slid open the fusuma and stealthily
entered Karin's room.

Whoa there, don't raise your voice. You'll startle everyone
in the other rooms awake. I'm just a traveler staying in the
next room over.
--Eh? A guest? Why are you in my room?

Young lady, you might not know this because you're young,
but this is what's called a 'night crawling' visit.

Y... Night crawling...! (I've heard about this from Oei-san.
What should I do...!)

I passed by you before going to bed and... I fell for you at
first sight. It's a bit embarrassing at my age. Would you
let me hold you just for tonight?
夜這いを受け入れる\c[27]【Ｈイベント】\c[0]

I don't mind♪ Despite appearances, I'm not averse to matters
of pleasure...

What!? That's unexpected. I didn't think you'd be so
willing. Anyway, I'm grateful. Then I'll take you up on that
offer\I[15]
Mmm...\I[15] Please come into the futon...\I[15]

--Karin took the hand of the man who came for a night visit
and led him to the futon.

\c[27]Main event count +5, vaginal ejaculation +3, external
ejaculation +2, lewdness +10\c[0]
I'm sorry! I'm not in the mood for this...

...Is that so. If a man is turned down during a night
crawling, he should leave quietly as per etiquette. Sorry
for waking you up from a good sleep. Farewell then...

--The man who came for a night visit hung his head in
disappointment and quietly slid the fusuma open and closed
again, then left for the late-night corridor.

...(Did I do something wrong? But it's rude to come to
someone's room while they're sleeping... Anyway, let's go
back to sleep... Yawn...)
--Karin yawned deeply and went back to bed once more...

...You seemed to have quite the fun last night. I could hear
the guest's voice all the way outside the inn.

--Eh!? Really!? Ahaha...! I'm sorry for causing such a
commotion...! (It seems like they found out about the night
visit...)

Tomorrow will be my first time in Edo. It must be a big
city, I'm so excited.

The room next door last night was so noisy with all the
moaning. It woke me up in excitement... and now I'm
suffering from lack of sleep...

I'm about to head back to my hometown. The pleasure quarters
of Edo were as wonderful as the rumors say. I plan to boast
about it when I return to my province.

Something happened in the next room in the middle of the
night...? I was surprised to hear a woman's loud voice.

Cheap inns are no good with their thin walls... I couldn't
get much sleep because of the noisy guests.

I came from Shinano as a peddler. Ever since this Shinjuku
was established, it's become very convenient to come to Edo
without rushing. In the past, if there were no inns and you
happened to injure your foot, you'd have to camp outdoors.

I could hear the moans of a young woman in the middle of the
night... It got me excited, despite my age\I[15]

...(The sounds from last night, the other guests must have
heard them clearly... Ugh, it's so embarrassing to think
about it now...)

(She's got a cute face and big boobs... I wanna hold her
tight...\I[15])

...? (It feels like someone is staring at me from the corner
of their eye...)

The old inn I used to frequent has closed down, so I've been
staying here recently.
